<parameternamelist>
<parametername>simulator</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The initialised DES simulator whose <computeroutput>Machines</computeroutput> array determines how many prefabs to spawn. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
